html.htmlText:
Service animals aren’t pets, so there’s no need to add them here.

Traveling with an emotional support animal? Check out our accessibility policy.

Ready for an LA adventure? Step into our palm tree paradise in Leimert Park, where sunshine and good vibes are always in the forecast! Just 10 mins from USC, and close to world-class attractions like museums, the Coliseum, Staple Center, and Sofi Stadium. Plus, if you're a shopaholic, we're near LA Live, Century Center, Beverly Hills Mall, and Santa Monica Promenade. Your unforgettable LA experience starts right here, in our delightful, sun-soaked home!

Get ready to unwind in our spacious bedroom, complete with a dreamy queen-size bed, a cool computer desk, a Smart Roku TV, and more outlets than you can shake a stick at! Sleep easy on hypoallergenic sheets and pillows, and snuggle up in our super-soft towels. Oh, and don't forget the gigantic private bathroom with an epic shower - it's all part of the package!

Full access to your bedroom and private bathroom, kitchen area for the coffee station, and microwave.

Parking is also available. Street parking or you can park on the driveway.
We are here if you need us. Available via text or if you see us around.

There are 2 small dogs in the house.

My mother or I will personally meet every guest to answer any questions.

section.subtitle: AirCover is comprehensive protection included for free with every booking.

features.title: Booking Protection Guarantee
features.subtitle: In the unlikely event a Host needs to cancel your booking within 30 days of check-in, we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Check-In Guarantee
features.subtitle: If you can’t check into your home and the Host cannot resolve the issue, we’ll find you a similar or better home for the length of your original stay, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Get-What-You-Booked Guarantee
features.subtitle: If at any time during your stay you find your listing isn't as advertised—for example, the refrigerator stops working and your Host can’t easily fix it, or it has fewer bedrooms than listed—you'll have three days to report it and we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: 24-hour Safety Line
features.subtitle: If you ever feel unsafe, you’ll get priority access to specially-trained safety agents, day or night.

content.htmlText:
Situated in the center of everything trendy in LA. You will be within a short driving distance of the most popular attracts Los Angeles has to offer.

You will be close to all the professional sports stadiums. We are less than 5 miles from Sofi Stadium, 5 miles to USC, Banc of California Stadium or Staple Center, and only 8 miles to Dodger Stadium.

If shopping is your reason to visit LA we're 7 miles from LA Live and Downtown LA, Century Center, Beverly Hills Mall, and 11 miles from Santa Monica 3rd Street promenade.

Shop & Eat at one of the 114 nearby stores and restaurants. Get a taste of LA soul food from Dulan's Soul Food or Chef Marilyn's, Queen of Down Home Southern Goodies. If you've never tired Phillips Bar-B-Que, then you need to make this place a destination on your bucket list. Love blues, then you need to visit the California Jazz and Blues Museum located less than 1 mile. Take the Finest in City transportation to all your destinations in the Crenshaw District.

section.title: Things to know
section.houseRulesSubtitle: You'll be staying in someone's home, so please treat it with care and respect.

html.htmlText:
As a host, my aim is to ensure that you have as comfortable a stay as you possibly can. I want you and your guests to create lasting memories during your stay in our home.

But to do so, I would really appreciate it if you could follow the below house rules. I know, I know, rules are boring… But these rules ensure we can provide future guests with a great experience.


- No smoking/ Vaping - with 25ft of the property
- Kitchen for reheating only, making tea or coffee 
- The washer and dryer are off-limits
- Please limit your showers to under 10 minutes ( we're in a drought)
- No outside visitors, no overnight guests
- No Parties/Events/Gatherings
- Do not engage in illegal activities anywhere on the property
- Pick up after yourself
- Please take the trash out before you leave
- Keep noise to a minimum after 11 pm
- Please do not rearrange our furniture
